This paper discusses a theoretical framework for self-paced learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions the use of regularized penalties, which is a common technique in statistical learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
